summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Fifteen ($1500.) Hundred dollars, from the General Fund of The City of Seattle, for the purpose of assisting in the construction of a wooden box or pope culvert on seventh Avenue Northwest, from West Fifty-fifth Street to West Sixty-fifth Street, in connection with the grading and curbing of Seventh Avenue Northwest, et al, as authorized by Ordinance No. 20425, creating Local Improvement District No. 2020.
